PatientDimSourceData

The PatientDim source data dimension contains information about records from PatientDim as they exist in a specific source. Each row represents a record from PatientDim from a source for a date range.

Properties

Reporting table name
dbo.PatientDimSourceData
Granularity
A record from the primary reporting table per source
